                     <interp inst="t18120916-22-person260" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . It is Mr. Simmon's property. It cost us sixteen shillings, that was lent on it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. There was a young man waiting outside, he gave me the coat.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 12,</p>
               <p>Of <rs id="t18120916-22-verdict126" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18120916-22-verdict126" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
